<doc>
  <member name="D3D12_TEX1D_DSV">
    <summary>
      <para>Describes the subresource from a 1D texture that is accessible to a depth-stencil view.</para>
    </summary>
    <remarks>
      <para>Use this structure with a <see cref="D3D12_DEPTH_STENCIL_VIEW_DESC" /> structure to view the resource as a 1D texture.</para>
    </remarks>
    <seealso href="https://docs.microsoft.com//windows/desktop/direct3d12/direct3d-12-structures">Core Structures</seealso>
  </member>
  <member name="D3D12_TEX1D_DSV.MipSlice">
    <summary>
      <para>The index of the first mipmap level to use.</para>
    </summary>
  </member>
</doc>